author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Rand Capital Reports Qtrly Basic And Diluted Net Increase In Net Assets From Operations Per Share $0.04
text:
March 8 (Reuters) - Rand Capital Corp:
* RAND CAPITAL ANNOUNCES FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 RESULTS
* RAND CAPITAL CORP - QTRLY BASIC AND DILUTED NET INCREASE IN NET ASSETS FROM OPERATIONS PER SHARE $0.04
* RAND CAPITAL CORP - REPORTED $5.05 NET ASSET VALUE (NAV) PER SHARE AT DECEMBER 31, 2017, COMPARED WITH $5.01 AT SEPTEMBER 30, 2017 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
